Title: Nyah Harmonious Ylang Ylang Handmade Bar(100 g)
Description: You are tired of your lifeless complexion and you are search of a natural soap which can effectively revive dull complexion. This organic bathing soap gives you silky soft skin within a few days of regular use. Made from a combination of herbal components like Ylang Ylang, Vegetable Oil, Butter and Glycerine, the Nyah Harmonious Ylang Ylang Handmade Bar can be an ideal solution most of your skin problems. The Ylang Ylang extract present in this natural soap bar is an exotic herb which is infused with antiseptic properties which keep your skin away from the attack of external impurities and microbes to prevent acne and blemishes, keeping your complexion flawless and purified. Ylang Ylang is also known to calm your senses with its soothing scent. In addition, your complexion will be nourished to the maximum extent, as the Vegetable Oil in this natural handmade soap provides the required amount of vitamins and minerals to your skin to promote the growth of healthy skin cells. Additionally, the Harmonious bathing soap also cleanses your skin by purging out the pores to rid them of impurities. Also, with the Butter extract in this smoothening your skin, your skin will be made touchably smoother.
CategoryName: Health and Beauty>Bath and Spa>Soaps

Title: Gluta-C White and Firm Soap(90 g)
Description: Gluta White And Firm Soap - 90gm:Formulated and developed by dermatologists, Gluta Advance White & Firm Soap offers the combined beauty and health giving benefits of Glutathione, L-Carnithine and Lipofirm---working in synergy to visibly lighten skin tone and progressively retexturize skin for a fairer, firmer, well-toned look.Direction for Use:Wet skin, gently massage soap on the skin, DO NOT RUB, avoid getting into eyes, nose or mouth. Let it sit for just a few seconds (First time user: just wash regularly). Then rinse thoroughly with cold water, leaving residue will cause skin to itch and feeling sore. IMPORTANT: Apply moisturizer generously after, all skin whitening soaps tends to dry the skin as part of the exfoliation process. Sun block is A MUST.

The appliance should be checked at least every two years, if find the equipment’s error that exceeds the technical data, must be recalibrated.2. To clean your sphygmomanometer use a clean soft cloth.3. Do not immerse the equipment in liquids to clean it.4. Do not hot sterilize.

Description: Recommended by hair transplant surgeons and hairdressers, Looks21 Hair Fibers is an effective totally natural solution for hair loss. Fibers from this plant have surface optical properties that are very similar to human hair. This is one of the reasons why Looks21 Hair Fibers gives users perfectly natural look. Moroccan Gossypium Herbaceum fibers tend to negatively charged while human hair tends to be positively charged. Therefore Looks21 Hair Fibers bond to your hair 200% stronger than regular hair building fibers. Natural mineral-based colorants virgin moroccan gossypium herbaceum is grayish white. The fibers are dyed into various colors to match human hair colors. Thanks to the micro-structure of Gossypium Herbaceum its fiber can be easily dyed with mineral-based colorants - iron oxides harvested from nature.
